Villa Rosa Kempinski recently held a wedding fair to showcase some of the services need in wedding preparation. Kavitha Mwanzia, a panelist, said a good wedding creates good memories, hence people should always aim for the best. The chief guest of the event was Tourism CS Najib Balala. "I am happy and amazed at how people take weddings seriously these days. I have been married for 32 years and I have two grandchildren. It is very important and a blessing as well," he said.